title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 1 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 1 2021
description:
Syndicated radio host Jesse Kelly joins Clay and Buck, talks California vax mandate for kids, congressional budget negotiations. Newsom mandates vaccines for children over 12. Open Line Friday calls. Senator Tommy Tuberville psychs up Buck for his first SEC game, discusses the budget.
